name: VoiceFirstFM
0:
”Alexa, ask VoiceFirst FM for the latest news”
”Text that to me”

Developer Terms of Use
des:
Stay up to date on the latest news from VoiceFirst FM. With this skill you can...

* Hear the latest VoiceFirst FM Facebook posts
* Have any post texted to your phone

A great way to keep informed using just your voice.
